;Darcwolf's Home
NUMBER 1902
NAME Darcden
FIXED_LIGHT
CAVE
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
You see a small cave carved into the trunk of a large tree. Comfortable
looking cushions have been laid out along one wall. The walls are smoothe
and decorated with primative artwork. A small firepit draws your attention
to the center of the room. A small basin of water sits near the firepit.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 3499
EXIT D 206
ITEM 0 1398 ADJ1=294 ADJ3=126 
EXTEND 0 burning brightly in the center of the room
ITEM 1 420 
EXTEND 1 decorated with primative artwork
ITEM 2 554
EXTEND 2 filled with magically cooled water
ITEM 3 198 ADJ1=77 ADJ2=56
;
NUMBER 1903
NAME Bacca's Cantina
CALL 33
FORGE
INDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
When you first step into the cantina you can hardly see anything while you
wait for your eyes to adjust to the light. Along the back wall you see a bar
with a man standing behind it rubbing a non-existent spot with a white towel.
There are many patrons scattered here and there around the room, none of them
look human. This is a place that is very dangerous if you are unexperienced.
You hear an alien music playing in the background, as a dancer gyrates on the
floor.
*DESCRIPTION_END

ITEM 0 1342
;BAR/HIDDEN
ITEM 1 1486 
;TABLE
ITEM 2 1800
;CHAIR
ITEM 3 1966
;PIANO

VARIABLE CHYEVENT
NUMBER 3499
NAME Chyme's Wagon
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
FOREST
*DESCRIPTION_START
You see a tiny clearing on a forested slope; a small gypsy wagon rests under
some oak trees. Sounds of soft chimes fill the air at every breeze. There is
a quilt and some pillows lying in a pile next to the wagon. The remains of a
carefully tended fire lies in the center of the grove.
*DESCRIPTION_END
